Class CornerPoint2D

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.geom.Point2D
      • movingmorphingmasking.data.topology.CornerPoint2D
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CornerPoint2D.Immovable, CornerPoint2D.LineSlider, CornerPoint2D.Movable

    public abstract class CornerPoint2D
extends java.awt.geom.Point2D
    The CornerPoint2D class defines a Point2D.Double.

    This class is only the abstract superclass for all points with unlimited or limited possible 2D coordinates. The actual location settings of the coordinates is left to the subclass.
